/>\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 同埋我諗INTJ普遍來講比 ENTJ  更鐘意 conceptulize 啲嘢, 揾事物的 特質, function, 比較uniqueness, meaning.  等等. <br />\n<br />\n3.  INTJ 的笑話比EＮTJ 賤, 同鐘意dark humor"},{"pid":"1b31b1b553f462c3e79fa1a2cfe2e7d75c109aef","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"點睇lntp"},{"pid":"8740ec6e8e36abbf05c5f377feaf5658dfe3c957","tid":2513351,"uid":222642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b31b1b553f462c3e79fa1a2cfe2e7d75c109aef","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"點睇lntp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"毒中之毒"},{"pid":"2d9fce3b871d104beff37753bb87b195b24d7202","tid":2513351,"uid":379493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b31b1b553f462c3e79fa1a2cfe2e7d75c109aef","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"點睇lntp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"一生最愛"},{"pid":"a33107177157e0e5bf8201c389358eef50796045","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d9fce3b871d104beff37753bb87b195b24d7202","tid":2513351,"uid":379493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b31b1b553f462c3e79fa1a2cfe2e7d75c109aef","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"點睇lntp"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"一生最愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"粟米肉粒飯"},{"pid":"676a8f1af2df40a2de11454412b84f1f88ea299b","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8740ec6e8e36abbf05c5f377feaf5658dfe3c957","tid":2513351,"uid":222642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b31b1b553f462c3e79fa1a2cfe2e7d75c109aef","tid":2513351,"uid":191410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"點睇lntp"},"cit